sequence-diagram

title Vox AI RAG Logic (Detail)

User [icon: user, label: "Usuário", color: blue]
App [icon: streamlit, label: "Orquestrador (Python)", color: orange]
LLM [icon: google-gemini, label: "Gemini (Geração)", color: purple]

DB [icon: supabase, label: "Supabase Vector Store", color: green]
Embedder [icon: google-gemini, label: "Google Embeddings API", color: purple]

User > App: "O que é PREP?"
App > Embedder: 1. Gera Embedding da Pergunta
Embedder > App: 2. Retorna Vetor [0.1, 0.5, ...]
App > DB: 3. RPC: match_documents(vetor)
DB > App: 4. Retorna Texto Relevante
App > LLM: 5. Monta Prompt + Contexto
LLM > App: 6. Resposta Fundamentada
App > User: Exibe Resposta